The Enterprise Architecture team should be engaged in the first instance by sending an email to the [EA team](mailto://ea-team@ea.finance-ni.gov.uk).

The Enterprise Architecture team must be engaged when:-
- Creating a business case (if not already engaged)
- At the beginning of Discovery of the [GDS agile lifecycle](https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/agile-delivery).
- At the beginning of Beta phases of the [GDS agile lifecycle](https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/agile-delivery).
